author: GameSpot
description:
Live from YouTube Theater in Los Angeles, see what's next in video games at #SUMMERGAMEFEST, hosted by Geoff Keighley. A 2 hour live showcase featuring updates from the world's top game development studios.  The Summer Game Fest show will be immediately followed by Day of the Devs, a look at upcoming indie games.

Stick around for the GameSpot pre and post-show.
title: SUMMER GAME FEST 2025
